@startuml
actor "User" as User
participant "Web Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong)" as Kong
participant "Document Service" as DocumentService
database "Document DB" as DocumentDB
participant "Cloudflare R2" as R2
queue "RabbitMQ\n(Celery Broker)" as RabbitMQ

== Luồng nghiệp vụ: Tải lên tài liệu cá nhân ==

User -> Frontend: Chọn file tài liệu
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Kong: POST /code-document-service/documents/upload\nmultipart/form-data: file
activate Kong
Kong -> DocumentService: Chuyển tiếp file và user_id
activate DocumentService

opt ENVIRONMENT != development
DocumentService -> DocumentDB: Kiểm tra UserSubscription\nis_active=true và period_end >= now
activate DocumentDB
DocumentDB --> DocumentService: Subscription hợp lệ hoặc null
deactivate DocumentDB
end

alt #F2F4F7 Không có subscription hợp lệ
DocumentService --> Kong: HTTP 403 Forbidden
Kong --> Frontend: Từ chối upload
Frontend --> User: Yêu cầu nâng cấp gói thuê bao
else Được phép upload
DocumentService -> DocumentService: validate_upload_file\nget_file_hash_and_size
DocumentService -> DocumentDB: INSERT Document\nstatus=UPLOADED, has_file=false
activate DocumentDB
DocumentDB --> DocumentService: doc_id
deactivate DocumentDB

DocumentService -> R2: Upload file gốc\n{user_id}/document/{doc_id}{ext}
activate R2
R2 --> DocumentService: Upload OK
deactivate R2

DocumentService -> DocumentDB: UPDATE has_file=true
activate DocumentDB
DocumentDB --> DocumentService: OK
deactivate DocumentDB

DocumentService -> RabbitMQ: send_task(process_document_task,\nargs=[doc_id], queue=CELERY_QUEUE_NAME)
activate RabbitMQ
RabbitMQ --> DocumentService: Task accepted
deactivate RabbitMQ

DocumentService --> Kong: HTTP 200 {doc_id, filename, status}
deactivate DocumentService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả kết quả upload
deactivate Kong
Frontend --> User: Hiển thị tài liệu đang xử lý nền
end

deactivate Frontend
@enduml
